The paper discusses automated verification techniques for identifying hardware security vulnerabilities, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves microarchitecture-specific programs and domain-specific languages, which are related to computer architecture (cs.AR). The tool developed by the authors involves synthesizing programs, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses cache coherence protocols, which is related to computer systems (cs.SY).
